Table.name: AUTHORIZATION_OBJECTS
Table.commentInRDBMS:
Table which includes all authorization objects with full history. Authorization object can be any business objects which is going to be secured, for example:
Fund with id 8657, or DataSet which defines 3 columns from PORTFOLIO_HOLDINGS_TB table, etc. It can be anything from the high-level perspective which can be somehove defined by Columns or Rows in the FORCE database.
